user.biography:
Welcome to my world 💁🏼‍♀️
♥ Designer & Owner @tahirabykb & @taijacollection

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by KALI BURNS on September 19, 2021 tagging @fitjeans. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text: You only miss the shots you don’t take 🖤

Built my own gym 😝😝 May the waist get flatter and ass get fatter 🙏🏼 Wearing new @tahirabykb Luxe leggings launching Sept 22nd 💜🤍
-
-
Okaaay these lockdowns are officially driving me crazy! Built a badass gym so I can keep training and feeling good.
